paragraphs.context: Dzikowo [d͡ʑiˈkɔvɔ] (German: Dieckow) is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Barlinek, within Myślibórz County, West Pomeranian Voivodeship, in north-western Poland. It lies approximately 6 kilometres (4 mi) west of Barlinek, 18 km (11 mi) east of Myślibórz, and 60 km (37 mi) south-east of the regional capital Szczecin.
